        "Description": "Last night your client Emma Carlisle murdered her uncle Zachary Carlisle. She has enlisted your help to cover up her murder and requests you deal with Rosie and Patrick who spotted her sneaking around last night, London PI Phinas Whitmer who if left alive will solve the case and prove Emma&apos;s guilt, a gardener named Oliver who is skeptical of his suicide and Rebecca Carlisle who suspects Emma.\r your client has requested that their deaths appear accidental but the type of accident is up to you",
